  <title>Puzzles</title>
  <p>Puzzles are divided into three categories namely, <gui>HuaRong
  Trail</gui>, <gui>Challenge Pack</gui> and <gui>Skill Pack</gui> based on the
  difficulty level of the game. The <gui style="button">Next Puzzle</gui> and
  <gui style="button">Previous Puzzle</gui> helps you to navigate
  sequentially.</p> 

  <section id="new-puzzle">
    <title>Play a new Puzzle</title>
      <p>To play a new puzzle:</p>
        <steps>
          <item><p>Click on <gui style="button">Puzzles</gui> on the top
          left.</p></item>
          <item><p>You can select a category and a puzzle by double clicking on
          it.</p></item>
        </steps>
  </section>

